    "### 2.40\n",
    "\n",
    "Show that $\\lceil \\log(n+1) \\rceil = \\lfloor \\log n \\rfloor +1 $"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Assume that $\\log(n)$ here mean $\\log_2(n)$. We only need to take care 3 cases:\n",
    "\n",
    "- $2^k < n < 2^{k+1} - 1$\n",
    "- $n + 1 = 2^{k+1}$\n",
    "- $n = 2^{k+1}$\n",
    "\n",
    "It's easy to verify that the equation hold for all 3 cases."
   ]
  }
